-- Bordier Sees Fewer New Customers in 2012, Le Temps Says
-- B y   S i m e o n   B e n n e t t
-- 2012-05-01T10:43:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-01/bordier-sees-fewer-new-customers-in-2012-le-temps-says.html
Bordier & Cie. expects the number of
new customers it attracts this year to be “a little more
modest” than in 2011, Le Temps  reported .  Assets under management were 10 billion Swiss francs ($11
billion) in April, compared with 9.8 billion francs at the end
of December, the newspaper said, citing the Geneva-based bank.  To contact the reporter on this story:
